{"tid":1508910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【前線全部入】 係男人嘅同我入撚晒黎！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-26T16:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T02:52:53.000Z","uid":253232,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"78a328039f3c0b8cc89d3ef41ff490cefef37e28","tid":1508910,"uid":253232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:05:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">好欣賞每個勇敢上前線嘅女義士，<br />\n你地每個都好勇敢，全部都人美心善</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以每次見到有女義士比狗捉撚咗，<br />\n都好撚心up好撚擔心，完全唔夠膽想像啲淫警會點對我地嘅女手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家啲撚樣大陸佬仲話要女女女 女手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母 <br />\n斬我係無問題！！！但搞佢地就一定唔撚得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">現在我正式呼籲</span></ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1:</span></span> 前線set好晒嘢，就一齊叫啲女仔行返後啲，比空間前線退又好，比空間自己都好，總之唔好比佢地走到最前！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2:</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">住荃灣、元朗、北角</span></span>高危地點嘅女義士，勇武、前線返去嘅時候，一定要同女義士組好隊，換好埋衫先返去，唔可以比任何一個落單！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3:</span></span> 如果仲見到啲撚樣企前線，影相握like、溝女就大大力屌啦，前線係真男人嘅地人，唔係比你地呢啲狗公溝女地方，呢家係抗爭吖！唔係交友遊戲！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後各位巴打，我地一齊做好覺悟，連身邊嘅婦孺都保護唔到，我地點樣保家吖！唔好再比個背脊比敵人！ </span></span><br />\n<br />\n以下都係為咗香港而被補